g.text: In this exercise you combine data by concatenating and joining tables.
Concatenate customer information data from the two different systems into one table
Convert the "Newsletter" column from number to string in the table from the system 1 (Number to String node)
Concatenate the customer data from the two systems (Concatenate node)
Join the information on the online purchases with the prices of the products
Join the "TransactionsOnline" and "ProductNrAndPrize" tables directly on the database (DB Joiner node)
Read the joined table into KNIME (DB Reader node)
Add the store location information to each purchase in a store based on the StoreID (Joiner node)
